OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,FConcern has been voiced around the
OL,7,Fmaintenance of schools across Northern
OL,8,FIreland with a repairs bill which
OL,9,F"could be up to #800m".
OL,11,FThe Stormont Assembly's Public
OL,12,FAccounts Committee has called for an
OL,13,F"urgent, system-wide reform of the
OL,14,Fschools' estate management and
OL,15,Fmaintenance".
OL,17,FThe committee published a report on
OL,18,FWednesday following their inquiry into
OL,19,Fmanaging the schools estate.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@VO]uD@AOUwD@LO]
