OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,FIt received evidence from officials
OL,7,Ffrom the Department of Education and
OL,8,FEducation Authority (EA), as well as
OL,9,Fwritten evidence from the Health and
OL,10,FSafety Executive NI.
OL,12,FThe report found that schools are in a
OL,13,Fstate of disrepair and that the
OL,14,Fcurrent situation is "unsafe", with
OL,15,Fsignificant maintenance backlogs that
OL,16,Fcould pose a health and safety risk
OL,17,Fand jeopardise educational outcomes
OL,18,Ffor young people.
OL,20,FThe committee made 11 recommendations
OL,21,Fas well as calling for urgent reform.
OL,26,@vD@VOUvD@]O]
