OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,FCommittee chair Daniel McCrossan
OL,7,Fcriticised the department and EA for
OL,8,Frelying on a "reactive, short-term
OL,9,Fapproach" and "poor governance".
OL,11,F"In the course of our inquiry, the
OL,12,Fcommittee heard that, 10 years on from
OL,13,Fthe formation of EA, poor
OL,14,Fcollaboration between it and the
OL,15,FDepartment of Education has continued
OL,16,Fto undermine the effectiveness of
OL,17,Festate management," the SDLP
OL,18,Frepresentative said.
OL,26,@pD@NOUqD@IO]qD@OOUqD@_O]sD@AOUyD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/16
