PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F446A1760699522
OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,F"During this time, these two
OL,7,Forganisations have operated without a
OL,8,Fclear plan and relied instead on a
OL,9,Freactive, short-term approach.
OL,11,F"This is an alarming example of poor
OL,12,Fgovernance that has failed to deliver
OL,13,Fvalue for money, meet the needs of
OL,14,Fschool users and has likely
OL,15,Fcontributed to the deterioration of
OL,16,Fsafety and quality across the estate.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/16
