OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F446A1760699522
OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,F"To compound problems further, there
OL,7,Fis a lack of reliable, up-to-date
OL,8,Fdata. Without robust information
OL,9,Fsystems, effective strategic planning
OL,10,Fis impossible, and performance cannot
OL,11,Fbe measured or improved."
OL,13,FMr McCrossan said there is currently
OL,14,Fno preventative maintenance plan and
OL,15,Falso backlogs relating to statutory
OL,16,Fremedial works, which he said are
OL,17,Festimated to cost around #29 million.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@YO]
