OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,FThe committee's recommendations
OL,7,Finclude that by early 2026, the
OL,8,Fdepartment develops and publishes a
OL,9,Fcomprehensive estate management
OL,10,Fstrategy, together with an associated
OL,11,Fannual delivery plan.
OL,13,FThey also called for the department
OL,14,Fand EA to review the roles and
OL,15,Fresponsibilities of all oversight
OL,16,Fmechanisms and put in place
OL,17,Fappropriate governance structures to
OL,18,Fensure that estate performance is
OL,19,Fregularly monitored.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/16
