OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,FAdditionally, the committee
OL,7,Frecommended clear plans are developed
OL,8,Fwithin 18 months by the department and
OL,9,FEA to ensure current special
OL,10,Feducational needs (SEN) provision is
OL,11,Ffit for purpose in advance of a
OL,12,Ftargeted capital investment plan to
OL,13,Fexpand the SEN provision across the
OL,14,Fschools' estate.
OL,16,FMr McCrossan added: "A modern, safe
OL,17,Fand inclusive school estate is not a
OL,18,Fluxury ` it is the fundamental right
OL,19,Fof every child in Northern Ireland.
OL,26,@xD@UOU
