OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,F"The department's current approach to
OL,7,Festate management is unsustainable,
OL,8,Fineffective and economically wasteful.
OL,10,F"There must be a new, collaborative
OL,11,Fworking relationship between the
OL,12,Fdepartment, the EA and
OL,13,Fschools."Listening to schools and
OL,14,Finvolving them earlier could lead to
OL,15,Ffaster, more informed responses to
OL,16,Fproblems.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@IOU
