OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F446A1760699522
OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,F"A new estate management strategy must
OL,7,Fbe developed and implemented without
OL,8,Fdelay."The school estate must be seen
OL,9,Fas a valued asset and a key enabler of
OL,10,Feducational success ` not just a
OL,11,Fcollection of buildings to be
OL,12,Fmaintained."
OL,14,FResponding, Education Minister Paul
OL,15,FGivan said the system is facing a
OL,16,F"capital funding crisis that must be
OL,17,Faddressed without delay".
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@GOUtD@LO]xD@AOUyD@XO]
