OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F446A1760699522
OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,F"I value the report's contribution in
OL,7,Fexposing the scale of the challenge,
OL,8,Fparticularly the chronic
OL,9,Funderinvestment in our schools' estate
OL,10,Fover many years," he said.
OL,12,F"The key issue here is not a lack of
OL,13,Fplanning, but a lack of funding.
OL,15,F"Severe and unsustainable financial
OL,16,Fpressures have left my department
OL,17,Funable to carry out routine
OL,18,Fmaintenance or invest in long-term
OL,19,Fimprovements.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@QO]tD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/16
