CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F446A1760699522
OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,F"Instead, we've had to stretch
OL,7,Fresources to cover only the most
OL,8,Furgent, health-and-safety-related
OL,9,Frepairs ` a reactive approach that, as
OL,10,Fthe report rightly highlights, cannot
OL,11,Fcontinue.
OL,13,F"Nowhere is the pressure more acute
OL,14,Fthan in special educational needs
OL,15,Fprovision.
OL,17,F"The cost of emergency SEN placements
OL,18,Fhas soared from #9 million in 2019 to
OL,19,Fa projected #85 million this year,
OL,20,Fwhich is an 850% increase in just six
OL,21,Fyears.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/16
