OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F446A1760699522
OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,F"That trajectory is simply not
OL,7,Ffinancially viable."Mr Givan added:
OL,8,F"Despite these constraints, I remain
OL,9,Fcommitted to improving the condition
OL,10,Fof our school estate.
OL,12,F"In line with one of the PAC's key
OL,13,Frecommendations, I have submitted a 10-
OL,14,Fyear, #1.7 billion special educational
OL,15,Fneeds investment plan to the Executive.
OL,17,F"This strategic proposal is designed
OL,18,Fto address long-term infrastructure
OL,19,Fneeds and ensure that children with
OL,20,FSEN are supported in appropriate, high-
OL,21,Fquality learning environments.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@TO]pD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/16
