OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F446A1760699522
OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,F"I am calling for urgent, cross-party
OL,7,Fsupport to secure the investment
OL,8,Fneeded to modernise and protect
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland's schools.
OL,11,F"Without action, our school estate
OL,12,Fwill continue to deteriorate, with
OL,13,Freal consequences for pupils, staff,
OL,14,Fand communities."
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the EA said they
OL,17,Fwelcome the report, which they said
OL,18,F"clearly reflects the scale of the
OL,19,Ffinancial challenges faced by the
OL,20,Feducation sector".
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUvD@QO]zD@AOU|D@QO]
