OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,F"Recurring shortfalls in budgets mean
OL,7,Fthat no funding is available for
OL,8,Froutine maintenance of the school
OL,9,Festate ` the only activity that can
OL,10,Fafford to be undertaken is that which
OL,11,Fseeks to avoid school closures and
OL,12,Fcarry out repairs urgently needed on
OL,13,Fpupil safety grounds," they said.
OL,15,F"This limited but unavoidable focus
OL,16,Finevitably leads to deterioration in
OL,17,Fthe condition of the estate.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@VO]wD@AOU
