OL,3,CConcern school repairs bill 'could be
OL,4,Cup to #800m'
OL,6,F"Despite these pressures, EA would
OL,7,Fassure pupils and parents that we are
OL,8,Ftaking decisive action in relation to
OL,9,Fthe #29 million statutory remedial
OL,10,Fbacklog referenced in the report.
OL,12,F"A #19 million programme of remedial
OL,13,Fworks has been prioritised for
OL,14,Fdelivery in the current financial
OL,15,Fyear, leaving a remaining shortfall of
OL,16,Faround #10 million, comprised
OL,17,Fprimarily of medium to low-risk
OL,18,Fremedial works.
